on the 9th , schuster attended the opening ceremony of shanghai office of the slovakian electric appliance design and research institute and toured shanghai city planning exhibition hall and shanghai museum .
the total trade volume of imports and exports between slovakia and shanghai has now reached 30 million us dollars with garments , pharmaceuticals , steel , furniture and auto parts as main commodities of trade on both sides .
schuster came to china on january 4 for a state visit at the invitation of china &apos;s president jiang zemin .
port of shanghai surpasses kaohsiung as world &apos;s fourth largest container port
xinhua news agency , shanghai , january 10 ( reporter feng yizhen ) news from the port industry indicated that last year the port of shanghai recorded a container throughput of 8.612 million teus against that of about 8.491 million teus completed by the port of kaohsiung in taiwan , surpassing the latter to become the world &apos;s fourth largest container port .
the global economic rebound and sustained economic growth in china last year have infused fresh vitality into the development of the port of shanghai .
in 2001 , the port of shanghai handled a container throughput of 6.34 million teus . last year its container throughput passed two milestones of 7 and 8 million teus to hit 8.612 million teus , a jump of 35.8 % over the previous year . its total cargo throughput reached 260 million tons , up 19 % over a year earlier while its foreign export volume exceeded 100 million tons for the first time by a 22 % increase over the previous year .
with a vast economic hinterland as its support and a huge network with direct links , the port of shanghai has become a hub with the largest number of liner routes and voyages .
at present , the port of shanghai has liner routes to all the 12 navigational zones on earth and trade relations with more than 400 ports in the world . it has daily voyages to europe and north america and weekly voyages to the mediterranean , the persian gulf , australia and so on .
the number of voyages to all parts of the world each month is more than 1,300 .
the container throughput of this year at the port of shanghai , which is speeding up the construction of its international shipping center , will exceed 9.5 million teus and efforts are made to reach 10 million teus so that the port will achieve its original goal one year ahead of schedule .
turkey allows us to inspect its bases
xinhua news agency , ankara , january 10 ( reporter huai chengbo ) according to the report of the turkish newspaper &quot; milliyet &quot; on the 10th , the turkish government has agreed to let 150 us military personnel to inspect the turkish bases and ports that may be used in the war against iraq .
