euro-zone trade surplus rose to 102.3 billion euros last year
xinhua news agency , brussels , february 19 ( reporter feng jian ) according to the latest statistics report released by eurostat on the 19th , due to the sharp drop in imports , the euro-zone posted an external trade surplus of 102.3 billion euros in 2002 , an increase of more than double over the preceding year .
